clinical_trials.eligibility_criteria:
Inclusion Criteria:

* Women had CS under spinal anesthesia;
* Women started to complain of PDPH;
* Women were free of exclusion criteria.

Exclusion Criteria:

* Women had prior history of PDPH or headache for any cause;
* Women had essential hypertension;
* Women with previous history of habitual

Inclusion Criteria:

* elective surgery for lobectomy or segmentectomy

Exclusion Criteria:

* local allergy to anesthetics;
* patients with a clear preoperative history of nervous system and mental system diseases or long-term use of sedatives or antidepressants;
* history of alcoholism, drug abuse
